+// 読み行を判定（アルファベット始まり→アルファベット索引、かな/カナ始まり→五十音、漢字はスラッグのローマ字から推定）
+function getIndexKey(postId: string, titleFirstChar: string): string {
+  // ASCIIアルファベット始まり → アルファベット索引
+  if (/[A-Za-z]/.test(titleFirstChar)) return titleFirstChar.toUpperCase();
+
+  // カタカナ始まり → 行マッピング
+  const kataMap: Record<string, string> = {
+    'アイウエオ': 'あ',
+    'カキクケコガギグゲゴ': 'か',
+    'サシスセソザジズゼゾ': 'さ',
+    'タチツテトダヂヅデド': 'た',
+    'ナニヌネノ': 'な',
+    'ハヒフヘホバビブベボパピプペポ': 'は',
+    'マミムメモ': 'ま',
+    'ヤユヨ': 'や',
+    'ラリルレロ': 'ら',
+    'ワヲン': 'わ',
+  };
+  for (const [chars, row] of Object.entries(kataMap)) {
+    if (chars.includes(titleFirstChar)) return row;
+  }
+
+  // 漢字・その他 → スラッグのローマ字から推定
+  const romaji = postId.replace(/^\d{8}-glossary-/, '').toLowerCase();
+  const s3 = romaji.slice(0, 3);
+  const s2 = romaji.slice(0, 2);
+  const s1 = romaji.slice(0, 1);
+
+  if (['shi','sha','shu','she','sho'].includes(s3)) return 'さ';
+  if (['chi','cha','chu','che','cho','tsu'].includes(s3)) return 'た';
+
+  if (['ka','ki','ku','ke','ko','ga','gi','gu','ge','go','ky'].includes(s2)) return 'か';
+  if (['sa','si','su','se','so','za','zi','zu','ze','zo'].includes(s2)) return 'さ';
+  if (['ta','ti','te','to','da','di','du','de','do'].includes(s2)) return 'た';
+  if (['na','ni','nu','ne','no'].includes(s2)) return 'な';
+  if (['ha','hi','hu','fu','he','ho','ba','bi','bu','be','bo','pa','pi','pu','pe','po'].includes(s2)) return 'は';
+  if (['ma','mi','mu','me','mo'].includes(s2)) return 'ま';
+  if (['ya','yu','yo'].includes(s2)) return 'や';
+  if (['ra','ri','ru','re','ro'].includes(s2)) return 'ら';
+  if (['wa','wo'].includes(s2)) return 'わ';
+  if (['a','i','u','e','o'].includes(s1)) return 'あ';
+
+  return s1.toUpperCase();
+}
